short_description: via verde transportes coletivos is a trucking and logistics company based in manaus, brazil.
long_description: desde 24 de novembro de 2007, a via verde transportes coletivos ltda presta serviço de transporte coletivo urbano na cidade de manaus. com cerca de 1.200 funcionários nos ajudam a atender os clientes com segurança, respeito e pontualidade de leste a oeste e de norte a sul. o nome da via verde transportes coletivos ltda, foi idealizado como forma de homenagear a maior floresta tropical do mundo – a floresta amazônica – e também, toda a sua biodiversidade.
business_tags: car carrier services | trucking and transportation
generated_description: via verde transportes coletivos ltda is a transportation company based in manaus, brazil. since november 24, 2007, they have been providing urban collective transportation services in the city of manaus. with approximately 1,200 employees, they prioritize safety, respect, and punctuality in serving customers from east to west and north to south. the company's name is inspired by the amazon forest, the largest tropical forest in the world and its biodiversity.
